    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve got to see this absolute beauty. It is in truly pristine, showroom condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels just like it did the day it rolled off the lot! It\u2019s been pampered and garage-kept, so you won't find a single blemish anywhere. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new and ready for the road, this is the one. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it\u2014come take a look, you're going to fall in love!",
