    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available now is an exceptional 997.2 Carrera S, a definitive driver\u2019s specification featuring the 3.8L naturally aspirated flat-six with Direct Fuel Injection (DFI). This powerplant delivers 385 hp through a tactile 6-speed manual transaxle and a factory-optioned limited-slip differential. The mechanical integrity is superlative; a recent DME report confirms zero over-revs in higher stages, and the cooling system has been proactively serviced to ensure thermal efficiency. The chassis utilizes Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) for variable damping, paired with four-piston monobloc calipers over cross-drilled rotors for fade-free deceleration. Finished in its original factory coat with consistent paint meter readings across all panels, this specimen exhibits no bolster wear or switchgear delamination. A concours-grade example for the discerning collector seeking mechanical purity.",
